    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/ddd038278d38f52828d06e2d9e84ebab.avif?t=1760084256\" width=620 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中共有 28 种 Boss 会以不同的方式对抗玩家。在激烈的战斗中，洞察 Boss 的动作、抓住破绽并逐渐提升操作手感，享受击败 Boss 的畅快感。一些 Boss 会在预设的三种特殊攻击中随机选择一种使用，因此即使是同一个 Boss，在不同轮次中也会展现出不同的模式，带来全新的战斗体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/6319c623b53dabceec5554b60f6978a3.poster.avif?t=1760084256\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/6319c623b53dabceec5554b60f6978a3.webm?t=1760084256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/6319c623b53dabceec5554b60f6978a3.mp4?t=1760084256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/aa7b5a47a5f8a37b00f8a08b53aa2b1a.avif?t=1760084256\" width=620 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个战斗机器人都拥有 5 种独特的被动技能和 3 种主武器，每种主武器都提供 2 条技能树。此外，还有 11 种副武器，它们同样拥有与主武器相同的 2 条技能树。玩家在升级时可以从给出的技能卡中选择，打造属于自己的技能构筑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/b251e218f5fa38df331771b2da4eadfa.poster.avif?t=1760084256\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/b251e218f5fa38df331771b2da4eadfa.webm?t=1760084256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/b251e218f5fa38df331771b2da4eadfa.mp4?t=1760084256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/20a3b818eac67f43ce112d03fbadc0eb.avif?t=1760084256\" width=620 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当无法躲避敌人的强力攻击，或想要一次性歼灭大量敌人时，请善用每个机器人独有的特技！通过关卡后出现的商店进行强化，或在升级时选择攻击力提升的技能卡来极大化威力，就能以更强大的攻击压制敌人。但请注意使用次数有限，充能可通过关卡后商店或敌人掉落的胶囊获得。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/7f5b460a8c0485d38eb938b5695ca2cd.poster.avif?t=1760084256\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/7f5b460a8c0485d38eb938b5695ca2cd.webm?t=1760084256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/7f5b460a8c0485d38eb938b5695ca2cd.mp4?t=1760084256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/e90938eed28e9a736fe12aef766e8770.avif?t=1760084256\" width=620 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗过程中击败敌人可以获得资源和道具。资源可用于升级机器人或强化特性，从而改变属性和独特的被动技能。道具则可以通过装备或强化来带来新的属性和技能，让你更好地迎战强大的 Boss 与敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/832c838d9f5fcdb4a5572a6903f6e6dd.poster.avif?t=1760084256\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/832c838d9f5fcdb4a5572a6903f6e6dd.webm?t=1760084256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/832c838d9f5fcdb4a5572a6903f6e6dd.mp4?t=1760084256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
